READ ME

SPLIT FASTA

Split fastas by sequence.

  bash fasta_split.sh /path/to/input.fasta /path/to/output_directory



MERGE CONTIGS

Merge smallest fasta sequences into a specified number of contigs with merged contigs seperated by a delimiter.

  python merge_contigs.py -fasta /path/to/fasta_directory


ADDITIONAL SETTINGS (MERGE CONTIGS ONLY)

  Flag                    Default             Description

  -contigs <number>       500                 specify merged contig number
  -delimiter <character>  N                   specify delimiter character
  -length <number>        500                 specify delimiter length
